Class ClusRuleFromTreeInduce

java.lang.Object
si.ijs.kt.clus.algo.ClusInductionAlgorithm
si.ijs.kt.clus.algo.rules.ClusRuleInduce
si.ijs.kt.clus.algo.rules.ClusRuleFromTreeInduce
public class ClusRuleFromTreeInduce extends ClusRuleInduce
Create rules by decision tree ensemble algorithms (forests). Use this by 'CoveringMethod = RulesFromTree' . This has to be own induce class because we need Clus instance for creating tree ensemble.
Author:
Timo Aho
